text: AM2 can refer to: * Socket AM2, a CPU socket for AMD desktop processors * Sega AM2, a research and development team for the video game company Sega * Arp- Madore 2, an open star cluster * a fictional element from The Sten Chronicles * Animusic * AM2 or AM², a yearly anime convention in its 2nd year held in Anaheim, California. * Achievement Measurement 2, a practical skills test required for becoming an electrician within Britain * British Rail Class 302, a class of Electric Multiple Units originally known as AM2 * Air mass 2, the solar spectra after passing through two atmosphere thicknesses.
title: AM2
